Style is what you make it – in life and at home. Get inspired. Find what you love. Make it yours.
Shop our feed:

node.text: This fall, join the (drama) club and go all in on larger-than-life shapes – like a showstopping canopy bed. Explore more via our link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joss & Main on August 22, 2021. May be an image of credenza.

node.text: This season, go for bold and dial up the drama with everything from statement furniture to dark accent pieces. See our story for more, then explore the full trend via our link in bio.

node.text: We live for a little drama, which is why starting tomorrow, we'll break down how you can embrace all things unexpected for fall.

node.text:
Staycation, vacation: Summer may be winding down, but you can re-create your favorite retreats at home, starting with your very own cocktail bar. Swipe for inspo from @themakerhotel and check out our story for more.

node.text: Want to turn your home into a post-summer getaway? Come back tomorrow for some fresh ideas for your mood board.

node.text: Style props // @michealadianedesigns, can you make our bedroom look this cozy too? Please and thank you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Joss & Main on August 15, 2021 tagging @designlovesdetail. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: The Fall Edit | We're living out our interior design dreams through @designlovesdetail’s styled nook, which serves up just the right amount of contrast. Love what you see? Explore our top trends (and styles) for the season via the link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joss & Main on August 14, 2021. May be an image of sofa and indoor.

node.text: We’ll be here all day wrapping up our summer reading list. Don’t send help.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joss & Main on August 13, 2021. May be an image of table.

node.text: Your patio deserves just as much attention as any other room inside your home. Agree? Make things extra inviting by starting with an anchor piece – like our Bogdan Striped Area Rug – and mixing and matching from there.
